description: The fairy elder goes to Pretty Cure Forest and prays in the corresponding temple. Lightning strikes the temple and the elder sees four Pickruns flying away. Meanwhile, in the human world, Love goes to the dance unit Trinity event. On the way, a huge monster called a Nakewameke appears, ruining the event. Love tries to protect her idol, Miyuki. Suddenly, the Pirun appears and goes to her mobile phone, transforming her into Cure Peach and allowing her to battle the monster.

titles.title: Freshly-Picked Fresh! Cure Peach Is Born!!
もぎたてフレッシュ! キュアピーチ誕生!!
